short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helps you manage code for all of your Laravel web-tinker tabs! Save/restore/organize your code

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you manage code for all of your Laravel web-tinker tabs: on each tinker-web domain you use (local or remote) you can save/restore/rename/delete organize your code into named snippets;

From the options page you can export all your snippets to .json, and re-import them.

Each snippet can be easily previewed (with nice PHP syntax highlighting) and restored into your Web-Tinker panel.

...messy tinker pages with oceans of commented code, no more!
